{"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK"]]},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBarcodeFormatGS1CompositeConfiguration"},"abstract":[{"text":"GS1 Composite configuration. Add to scanner configuration to scan GS1 Composite barcodes.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":"(SBSDKBarcodeFormatGS1CompositeConfiguration) "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBarcodeFormatGS1CompositeConfiguration"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When not enabled, the individual parts of GS1 Composite barcodes will be returned as separate items,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"if the respective formats are enabled (UPC-A, Code 128, MicroPDF417, PDF417)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Those barcode items will have their isGS1CompositePart field set to true."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If GS1 Composite scanning is enabled, the individual parts are never returned, even if their respective formats"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"are enabled, except when the linear component is a UPC or EAN barcode. In that case the linear component might still"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"occasionally be returned as a separate result. If this situation needs to be avoided, remove the UPC and EAN formats from"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the enabled formats."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If GS1 Composite scanning is disabled, but GS1 message validati